				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document} $$q_{i} = s_{i}\nu_{i}. $$ \end{document}qi=siνi.

We calculate the projections of each parameter, θi, onto each eigen-parameter, qj, as 
