				\begin{document} $$c_{ij} = \theta_{i} \cdot q_{j}. $$ \end{document}cij=θi·qj.

As a measure of the overall sloppiness of each parameter, l, we use the sum of the contributions of each parameter to the eigen-parameters, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
